Discover businesses in the historic city of Famagusta (Ammochostos). From its deep-water port to its ancient walled city, Famagusta is a center of commerce, tourism, and education.

Why Use Our Famagusta Directory?

Connect with the key sectors of this iconic port city:

  • Shipping & Logistics: Find companies operating out of one of the island's most important commercial harbors.
  • Tourism & Hospitality: Explore hotels, restaurants, and tour operators in this historically rich destination.
  • Retail & Services: Discover a wide range of shops and professional services that cater to the local population and visitors.

Start your search to connect with the diverse business community of Famagusta.
